Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait across all process variants where it occurs
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in Accepted + Wait when followed by Completed + Resolved compared to when followed by Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + Wait in variants that include Completed + In Call versus variants that do not
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Average time from Accepted + Wait to Completed + Resolved in cases where Completed + In Call appears earlier in the trace
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time between Queued + Awaiting Assignment and Accepted + Wait in variants containing Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Total duration of Accepted + Wait in traces that transition to Completed + In Call within the same case
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Time from Accepted + In Progress to Accepted + Wait in variants that later include Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Elapsed time between Accepted + Wait and the next occurrence of Accepted + In Progress when Completed + In Call is present in the variant
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Cycle time of Accepted + Wait in cases that eventually reach Completed + In Call versus those that end in Completed + Closed without any Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait grouped by country, specifically in traces containing Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country filtered by the function ma > 0 where ma is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + Wait in variants where Completed + In Call occurs before Accepted + Wait
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Total time from Accepted + Wait to Completed + Closed in process variants that include Completed + In Call after Accepted + Wait
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Time between Accepted + Wait and Completed + In Call when they appear consecutively or with only intermediate Accepted + In Progress events
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average duration of Accepted + Wait in high-frequency variants (frequency > 100) that also contain Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Elapsed time from case start to Accepted + Wait in variants where Completed + In Call is the first completed activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs
